<Link id="l00498" /><CodeLine lineNumber="498"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordtype">void</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> RISCVAsmPrinter::emitSled(</Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">const</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/machineinstr">MachineInstr</a> &#42;<a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/lib/codegen/globalisel/irtranslator-cpp/#abe44dfdea65b4f7e11e0a608ab708b76">MI</a>, SledKind Kind) &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00499" /><CodeLine lineNumber="499"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// We want to emit the jump instruction and the nops constituting the sled.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00500" /><CodeLine lineNumber="500"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// The format is as follows:</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00501" /><CodeLine lineNumber="501"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// .Lxray&#95;sled&#95;N</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00502" /><CodeLine lineNumber="502"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">//   ALIGN</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00503" /><CodeLine lineNumber="503"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">//   J .tmpN</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00504" /><CodeLine lineNumber="504"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">//   21 or 33 C.NOP instructions</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00505" /><CodeLine lineNumber="505"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// .tmpN</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00506" /><CodeLine lineNumber="506"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00507" /><CodeLine lineNumber="507"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// The following variable holds the count of the number of NOPs to be patched</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00508" /><CodeLine lineNumber="508"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// in for XRay instrumentation during compilation.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00509" /><CodeLine lineNumber="509"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Note that RV64 and RV32 each has a sled of 68 and 44 bytes, respectively.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00510" /><CodeLine lineNumber="510"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Assuming we&#39;re using JAL to jump to .tmpN, then we only need</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00511" /><CodeLine lineNumber="511"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// (68 - 4)/2 = 32 NOPs for RV64 and (44 - 4)/2 = 20 for RV32. However, there</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00512" /><CodeLine lineNumber="512"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// is a chance that we&#39;ll use C.JAL instead, so an additional NOP is needed.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00513" /><CodeLine lineNumber="513"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">const</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> uint8&#95;t NoopsInSledCount =</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00514" /><CodeLine lineNumber="514"><Highlight kind="normal">      <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/lib/codegen/globalisel/irtranslator-cpp/#abe44dfdea65b4f7e11e0a608ab708b76">MI</a>-&gt;getParent()-&gt;getParent()-&gt;getSubtarget&lt;<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/riscvsubtarget">RISCVSubtarget</a>&gt;().<a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/x86/lib/target/x86/disassembler/x86disassembler-cpp/#a652270ec0bdb03b5a7f934524412aa7f">is64Bit</a>()</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00515" /><CodeLine lineNumber="515"><Highlight kind="normal">          ? 33</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00516" /><CodeLine lineNumber="516"><Highlight kind="normal">          : 21;</Highlight></CodeLine>
